// Lake_heal_arm -- step 8: the reliability heal end-to-end (Reliable.g: inseq + retransmit + the adversary).
//  Stand up a FRESH isolated pair (Ivy/Jon) on a clean mock carrier -- isolated so the step-4 trial's
